</b><b>lecz już nie dla świata.</b>

00:29:07.480 --> 00:29:09.480 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<b>Cóż to za człowiek?</b>

00:29:09.880 --> 00:29:11.880 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<b>Umarły.</b>

00:29:12.599 --> 00:29:14.599 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<b>Patrz,</b>

00:29:14.680 --> 00:29:16.680 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<b>duch nadziei życie mu nadaje.</b>

00:29:18.480 --> 00:29:20.519 line:85% position:50% size:80%
