00:30:17.599 --> 00:30:19.599 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<b>Gustawie!</b>

00:30:19.680 --> 00:30:21.680 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<b>Anielski Gustawie!</b>

00:30:22.240 --> 00:30:24.440 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
